item.title: Honda's CB500X and NC700X ADV Adventure Bikes for 2016 | FIRST LOOK
item.description:
Honda's CB500X and NC700X ADV Adventure Bikes for 2016 | FIRST LOOK

Two more Honda X models returning for 2016 are the NC700X and CB500X, both with styling makeovers and other "important" updates, based on the short description provided to us. Based on the teaser images provided to us, the most obvious change are the taller windscreens on both models.

item.title: Honda Introduces 2016 VFR1200X Adventure Bike | FIRST LOOK
item.description:
Honda Introduces 2016 VFR1200X Adventure Bike | FIRST LOOK

How wrong we were to think Honda 's 2016 model lineup was complete, headlined by the all-new Africa Twin. Instead, Honda will add another X model to the line, the VFR1200X , known as the Crosstourer in other parts of the world.

item.title: 2016 DUCATI MONSTER 1200R | FIRST RIDE
item.description:
2016 DUCATI MONSTER 1200R | FIRST RIDE

They say: For those that make performance their lifestyle. We say: Another impressive R model for the Ducati history books. Please enable Javascript to watch this video When Ducati introduced the totally redesigned Monster 1200 in early 2014, the bike represented a paradigm shift for the 21-year-old model line.
